column5: I'm the big two four!
I'm 24 but my wife says i'm more immature than my son! (He's 2)
I am very young in my mind because I still play with toys.
58 going on 12

sigh*.....some believe that on the "other side" we will all either go forward or backward to the age that Jesus died...32....can you imagine....wwwwooooooohhhhooooooo  ...  no death for me yet please...too much left to do...but I sure can't wait for the day that I just don't give a carp...may even get a tattoo on my wringles...hehehe...and pretend that I have lost my mind....ya, carp my pants and all...with a cig hanging out of my mouth and flatulating everywhere...what a treat my boys are in for...

I don't think there is a generation gap when it comes to fishing...  I'm 72...next weekend I will be fishing with a 29 year old, a 38, a 44, a 62 and a 73...  We all have that one thing in common...we love to fish !!!
18...been on the board since 14
Its beginning to look like I'm Moses  I've taken younger ones than you fishing at times, so dont fret 'bout your age. so dive right in here, you are more than welcome.
your's too?? i thought mine was the only one!
Its beginning to look like I'm Moses  I've taken younger ones than you fishing at times, so dont fret 'bout your age. so dive right in here, you are more than welcome.
Hey all people on the fourms, are there any young anglers i can chat with. I mean jeez i got to make some friends here.
what's young to you?
I'm still just a baby... in my Mother's eyes!
I'm 26, but most of the people here are willing to be chatty with anyone, no matter what their age.
My wife keeps telling me i behave like a 12 year old  does that count
I'm 23,  but you can chat with anyone
your lucky mine say 10 for me!

Hah! Mine just rolls her eyes when she tells folks about me. I don't know why she always implies that I'm immature.  Well, my chores are done, so I'm gonna sneak over to the schoolyard with the new casting rig for some much needed practice. She still doesn't know about that acquisition.  JF
I'm 21
im 13
I still act like I'm 18!  Just ask my wife!!!!!!!  We're a young bunch at heart so dont be afraid to talk to any of us!!
I'm 20
if I'm 13 would that mean I'm the youngest on this forum perhaps?
I'm older than dirt, and the one lesson I have learned is to talk to people older than you because they tend to know more and do not mind sharing the knowledge.
I'm 50.... going on 18.
im 22
I'm 22 also
I'm 45 but really immature!
I'm immortal so I'll be around for ever
Perhaps, but just watch yer language so ya don't embarrass any of us old pharts. We're very sensitive here.  JF

One of you youngsters put him up this, didn't ya? Pretty cheesy way of rubbing it in that some of us are nearer the coffin than the cradle. After raking lawns all morning I really don't need any other reminders of my decrepitude.  JF
Hey  Im 21
18 here...
